individual_records.evidence_sentence: Case FBC090235 carried a BRCA2 germline pathogenic variant (c.574_575delAT; p.Met192ValfsX13) identified by germline testing.

variants.additional_notes: This variant was identified through germline testing and confirmed by WGS.
key_quotes: Case FBC090235 carried a BRCA2 germline pathogenic variant (c.574_575delAT; p.Met192ValfsX13) identified by germline testing.

individual_records.evidence_sentence: Non-BRCA1/2 case FBC060681 harboured a BRCA2 VUS (c.7828G>A p.Val2610Met).

functional_data.summary: The variant is in a highly conserved amino acid and is predicted to create a de novo donor splice-site in exon 17, although no experimental evidence supported this.
